data.name: AssociateDisbursementTransaction
data.value: update CKT_DISB_TRAN set INT_INTER_ID = @intInterId where (CPA_TYPE = @cpaType) and (CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (DISB_TRAN_ID = @disbTranId)

data.name: CreateDisbursementStatusHistory
CreateDisbursementTransaction1
CreateDisbursementTransaction2

CreateDisbursementTransactionRln
CreatePaymentStatusHistory
ReadDisbursement1
data.value: select top(1) sum(AMOUNT) from CKT_DISB_TRAN where (@prqGeneratedId = PRQ_GENERATED_ID) and (REFERENCE_NUMBER = @referenceNumber)

data.name: ReadDisbursement2
data.value: select CPA_TYPE, CSP_NUMBER, DISB_TRAN_ID, AMOUNT, PRQ_GENERATED_ID, REFERENCE_NUMBER from CKT_DISB_TRAN where (@prqGeneratedId = PRQ_GENERATED_ID) and (REFERENCE_NUMBER = @referenceNumber) and (@cpaType = CPA_TYPE) and (@cspNumber = CSP_NUMBER)

data.name: ReadDisbursementStatus
data.value: select top(1) DISB_STATUS_ID from CKT_DISB_STATUS where DISB_STATUS_ID = 2

data.name: ReadDisbursementTranRlnRsn
data.value: select top(1) DISB_TRN_RLN_RS_ID from CKT_DSB_TRN_RLN_RS where DISB_TRN_RLN_RS_ID = 1

data.name: ReadDisbursementType1
data.value: select top(1) DISB_TYPE_ID, CODE from CKT_DISB_TYPE where DISB_TYPE_ID = @disbTypeId

data.name: ReadDisbursementType2
data.value: select top(1) DISB_TYPE_ID from CKT_DISB_TYPE where DISB_TYPE_ID = 73

data.name: ReadInterstateRequest
data.value: select top(1) T1.IDENTIFIER from CKT_INTERSTAT_RQST T1 join CKT_INT_RQST_OBG T2 on (T1.IDENTIFIER = T2.INT_GENERATED_ID) and (@otyType = T2.OTY_TYPE) and (@obgGeneratedId = T2.OBG_GENERATED_ID) and (@cspNumber = T2.CSP_NUMBER) and (@cpaType = T2.CPA_TYPE)

data.name: ReadObligation
data.value: select top(1) CPA_TYPE, CSP_NUMBER, OB_ID, DTY_GENERATED_ID from CKT_OBLIGATION where (DTY_GENERATED_ID = @dtyGeneratedId) and (OB_ID = @obId) and (CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (CPA_TYPE = @cpaType)

data.name: ReadObligee
data.value: select top(1) CSP_NUMBER, TYPE, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TMST from CKT_CSE_PERSON_ACC where (CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (TYPE = 'E')

data.name: ReadPaymentRequestPaymentStatusHistory1
data.value: select T1.PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID, T1.AMOUNT, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.CSE_PERSON_NUMBER, T1.RECOVERY_FILLER, T1.TYPE, T1.PRQ_R_GENERATED_ID, T2.PST_GENERATED_ID, T2.PYMNT_STAT_HIST_ID, T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T2.CREATED_BY, T2.CREATED_TIMESTAMP from CKT_PMNT_REQUEST T1 join CKT_PMNT_STAT_HIST T2 on (T1.CSE_PERSON_NUMBER = @csePersonNumber) and (T1.TYPE = 'RCV') and (T1.PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID = T2.PRQ_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE = @discontinueDate) and (T2.PST_GENERATED_ID = 27) order by T1.AMOUNT desc

data.name: ReadPaymentRequestPaymentStatusHistory2
data.value: select T1.PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID, T1.AMOUNT, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.CSE_PERSON_NUMBER, T1.RECOVERY_FILLER, T1.TYPE, T1.PRQ_R_GENERATED_ID, T2.PST_GENERATED_ID, T2.PYMNT_STAT_HIST_ID, T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T2.CREATED_BY, T2.CREATED_TIMESTAMP from CKT_PMNT_REQUEST T1 join CKT_PMNT_STAT_HIST T2 on (T1.CSE_PERSON_NUMBER = @csePersonNumber) and (T1.TYPE = 'RCV') and (T1.PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID = T2.PRQ_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE = @discontinueDate) and (T2.PST_GENERATED_ID = 27) order by T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP desc

data.name: ReadPaymentStatus
data.value: select top(1) PAYMENT_STATUS_ID from CKT_PAYMENT_STATUS where PAYMENT_STATUS_ID = 23

data.name: UpdateCollection
data.value: update CKT_COLLECTION set DISB_DT = @disbDt, LAST_UPDATED_BY = @lastUpdatedBy, LAST_UPDATED_TMST = @lastUpdatedTmst, AR_NUMBER = @arNumber where (COLL_ID = @collId) and (CRT_TYPE = @crtType) and (CST_ID = @cstId) and (CRV_ID = @crvId) and (CRD_ID = @crdId) and (OBG_ID = @obgId) and (CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (CPA_TYPE = @cpaType) and (OTR_ID = @otrId) and (OTR_TYPE = @otrType) and (OTY_ID = @otyId)

data.name: UpdatePaymentRequest
data.value: update CKT_PMNT_REQUEST set AMOUNT = @amount where PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID = @paymentRequestId

data.name: UpdatePaymentStatusHistory
data.value: update CKT_PMNT_STAT_HIST set DISCONTINUE_DATE = @discontinueDate where (PST_GENERATED_ID = @pstGeneratedId) and (PRQ_GENERATED_ID = @prqGeneratedId) and (PYMNT_STAT_HIST_ID = @pymntStatHistId)
